  "translations": {
    "en": "So whoever was ignorant of him was ignorant of me, and whoever recognised him recognised me. Whoever denied his Imamate denied my prophethood, whoever denied his rulership denied my messengership. Whoever refuted his superiority lowered me, whoever fought him fought me, whoever insulted him insulted me, for he is from me, created from my clay. He is the husband of Fatima and the father of al-Hasan and al-Husayn.",
    "ur": "پس جو انہیں نہ جانے اس نے مجھے نہ جانااور جو انہیں پہچانے اس نے مجھے پہچانا۔",
    "tr": "Kim onu bilmezse beni bilmemiştir, kim onu tanırsa beni tanımıştır.",
    "fa": "پس هر کس او را نشناسد مرا نشناخته۔",
    "id": "Barangsiapa tidak mengenalnya, ia tidak mengenalku.",
    "bn": "যে তাঁকে চিনলো না সে আমাকে চিনলো না।",
    "es": "Quien lo ignore me ha ignorado, y quien lo reconozca me ha reconocido.",
    "fr": "Quiconque l'ignore m'a ignoré, et quiconque l'a reconnu m'a reconnu.",
    "de": "Wer ihn nicht kennt, kennt mich nicht.",
